============================== CMS CORE STANDARD DB SCHEMA (JWT ENABLED)==============================

[COMMON COLUMN STANDARD] 
id BIGINT PK created_at DATETIME NOT NULL
created_by BIGINT
updated_at DATETIME 
updated_by BIGINT 
